  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the investigators explore the possible role of DMSA to detect renal affection in diabetic
      &amp;/or hypertensive patients by detecting difference in counts using Tc 99m DMSA in control &amp;
      diabetic &amp;/or hypertensive patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
